  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can touch a weapon or up to 50 pieces of ammunition as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, giving it the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Frost\">frost</a>&nbsp;property for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your sorcerer level (minimum 1). At 9th level, you can confer the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Icy-Burst\">icy burst</a>&nbsp;property instead, but the duration of the power is halved. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>",
